	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I realized that instead of using HDMA to create the top and bottom bar, a better way would be to use BG3 to create the top and bottom bar.  This way would be better because the CPU can keep the PPU in forced-blank until DMAing is finished, even when it finishes late.

		

		</td>
